  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Kawsaqesniykitachus qhuyanki chayqa,
 Willaray Jesús salvasusqanta./
 
[V2]
 /Parlay Cristomanta; willay kawsaqesman,
 Cristo qanrayku wañusqanta./
 
[V3]
 /Willaramuy, willaramuy,
 Mayllapipis willay Jesusmanta./
 
